# Workbooks Manager — Tauri+Svelte build artifacts.
#
# Source-of-truth tree:
#   src/                         Svelte UI
#   src-tauri/src/               Rust shell (lib.rs, main.rs)
#   src-tauri/Cargo.toml         deps
#   src-tauri/Info.plist         custom Info.plist merged into bundle
#   src-tauri/tauri.conf.json    Tauri build config
#   src-tauri/build.rs, capabilities/, icons/

# Frontend build output — produced by `bun run build` (Vite).
dist/

# Bun lock — Bun resolves consistently across machines from package.json
# in this monorepo's setup; check this back in if reproducible installs
# become a pain point across contributors.
bun.lock
node_modules/

# Rust build artifacts.
src-tauri/target/

# Tauri codegen — recreated on each `tauri dev`/`tauri build`.
src-tauri/gen/

# Sidecar binaries — copies of workbooksd dropped here at release
# build time by the release pipeline (see release.sh). Reproducible
# from packages/workbooksd/, no need to track 14 MB of bytes.
src-tauri/binaries/
